tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE impressions (
    impression_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    impression_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    device_type VARCHAR(50),
    campaign_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE audience_metrics (
   id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   audience_name VARCHAR(255),
   age_range VARCHAR(50),
   gender VARCHAR(10),
   clicks INT,
   impressions INT
);

CREATE TABLE location_metrics (
   id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   location_name VARCHAR(255),
   city VARCHAR(50),
   country VARCHAR(50),
   clicks INT,
   impressions INT
);
